description: After a delicious gluten-free and vegetarian dish? This healthier beetroot and feta quiche recipe uses sweet potato for the crust.
keywords: Beetroot & Feta Quiche With Sweet Potato Crust
name: Beetroot & Feta Quiche With Sweet Potato Crust Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Scatter half the rocket over base. Whisk eggs and milk together in a medium bowl. Season with pepper. Pour egg mixture over rocket. Arrange beetroot and onion over top. Bake for 35 minutes or until egg mixture has set. Cool for 20 minutes. Top with feta and remaining rocket, season with pepper and serve.
